						               													<description>Dragon and Bandits is a fantasy-themed game in which the players are bandits who sneak around a sleeping dragon, trying to acquire treasure.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Cards accumulated can either be treasure, movement, or dragon movement cards. The treasure cards are saved until the end of the game and added up for points. The movement cards allow the character to move, but at the cost of making noise. As more noise is made, counters are removed from the dragon; if all the counters are removed, the dragon awakes, and every player in the dragon's line of sight must discard all treasure. Players can affect the dragon's line of sight by playing dragon movement cards.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game ends when the deck of sixty cards is empty, and whoever has the most accumulated treasure wins.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
